title: Pirater's tale
author: Pirater
pages:
#- Once upon a time, there was a ship which elegantly hovered over the crystal-clear ocean waves. §0
§0
§0The sea had thrown everything against the ship, but despite this, it had survived.§0
§0
§0This was about to change.
#- A menacing, blue squid with the name of "TTK2" emerged from the clouded waters - barnacled and aggressive. §0
§0
§0It took a swing at the ship, but the ship staggered backwards, and continued sailing towards its destination.
#- The fear on the crews faces were evident, as the squid kept doing shit that they didn't like.§0
§0
§0Then it turned out the destination was the squids mouth, so it got eaten the whole time and died.§0
§0
§0THE END
#- 